I have made several sales at good profits, and this represents my new list, not what I have been doing. I made 110 % on $550 in less than two weeks - and other profits nearly as good. This is recent. I've been making profits off end on ever since I started nearly a year ago. My credit balance now is between 5 and 6 thousand. I haven't my monthly balance sheet yet. 
Don't be fooled when the papers say that "the market" has declined. There isn't any market; there are only individual stocks and groups of stocks. My stocks generally rise when the high priced gambling stocks have a smash. <del/> I buy value, determined by earning power, and in the long pull I can't fail to profit most satisfactorily. 
Don't be worried over occasional drops in price all these will rise. 

